               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34069-5" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED:</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Neomycin and Polymyxin B Sulfates and Gramicidin Ophthalmic Solution USP is supplied in a plastic squeeze bottle with a controlled drop tip in the following size:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>10 mL – NDC 54868-6253-0<br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20110504"/>
               <component>
                  <section ID="i4i_storage_id_31697884-a627-4f0b-9a56-c2f0f0ced764">
